        010 (Summarize action seed — establishes the action-row template); 011
        (Summarize playbook config — establishes the playbook-row template); 012
        (`SessionSummarizeOrchestrator` — the reuse target for `/analyze`); 015
        (`InvokeSummarizePlaybookTool` — the wrapper template); 017
        (`StructuredOutputStreamWidget` — the widget being proven schema-driven);
