        template); 031 (Phase 2 verification — confirms baseline state of Summarize
        works end-to-end so `/analyze`'s measurement isn't confounded by Phase 2
        regressions). Confirm all 22 Phase 2 tasks ✅ at Step 1.
      </dependency>
    </dependencies>
