    <criterion testable="true">SC-19 cost target: total elapsed time from Step 0 START to Step 10 END is &lt; 1 day (8 hours) per spec SC-19 wording. Target ≤ 4 hours per plan.md Phase 3 estimate. Actual time recorded honestly even if &gt; target (this IS the measurement; honest failure is valid evidence).</criterion>
  </acceptance-criteria>
</task>
